race.comment: ALL IN OKIE (7) was prominent from the outset when second over 1207m at this track (Dirt) last time out. Another bold showing is expected. GET DREAMY (4) turned in a decent effort last start to finish second over 1609m at this track after being in the firing line on the bend. Finds a tougher race but a win is not out of the question. RYLO (3) is a three-year-old gelding on debut from the stable of William Bret Calhoun. By Flat Out from Jill Marie. A good gate is sure to assist. Bold showing expected. CODE MANDALORE (6) is close to breaking through after two consecutive placings, the latest coming when third over 1207m at this track (Dirt). Best figures measure up. Sure to run well.
